  The bug is that the Student structure was created but the [38;2;177;185;249mscores[39m array
  was never allocated memory, yet the [38;2;177;185;249madd_score[39m function assumes it exists
  and tries to write to it, causing a segmentation fault.

  TASK_COMPLETE
